data.description: Absolutely fantastic place to live! Amenities galore. 13 miles of trails, private community beaches, tennis courts, access to 3 lakes, docks, heated summer pool, boat launch, Pickleball courts/Baseball fields. New Roof, Home is located at the end of a cul-de-sac & is surrounded by trees, super private, quiet, peaceful serenity. 3 bdrms & 3 full baths. Home boast laminate wood flr's, carpet, ceramic tile, interior paint, Ceiling fans. Main level has Living rm, dining rm & kitchen, main bathrm and 3 bdrm's  primary has full bathrm. Lower level has huge family rm being used as primary bedrm, full bath & laundry rm. Nice deck leads to fully fenced backyard. 2nd deck area. Close to JBLM, Lacey, Olympia, Tacoma area. Make us an offer!
